
IMAPStore francojc@wfu.edu-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
User francojc@wfu.edu
PassCmd "pass francojc@wfu.edu"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
Timeout 120
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/cert.pem

MaildirStore francojc@wfu.edu-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /Users/francojc/.local/share/mail/francojc@wfu.edu/
Inbox /Users/francojc/.local/share/mail/francojc@wfu.edu/INBOX

Channel francojc@wfu.edu
Expunge Both
Far :francojc@wfu.edu-remote:
Near :francojc@wfu.edu-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"*fts-flatcurve*" !"*virtual*"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 1000
ExpireUnread no
# End profile

